    "description": "Guardião Tupã is a fantasy adventure set in a world where the creatures of the Brazilian folk are being threatened by the dreaded Dry Body, which seeks to break the balance and invade other worlds. On this journey, you take control of a newly created being using part of the energies of an ancient guardian. This being sets out to recover its strength and restore the balance, also learning more about this world and Brazilian culture in the process.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Explore a fantastic world</strong><br><br>An entity is threatening the kingdom and only the remnants of the old guardian can reverse the situation! Fight corruption and restore balance to the forest.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046400/extras/9622d6164758211b93e30133afebc725.poster.avif?t=1718141187\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046400/extras/9622d6164758211b93e30133afebc725.webm?t=1718141187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046400/extras/9622d6164758211b93e30133afebc725.mp4?t=1718141187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br></li><li><strong>Use your amber hook</strong><br><br>Your amber hook can do much more than just destroy, traverse great distances, and combine your skills to forge a brighter future.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046400/extras/25672758a6bd2aab40b8158699c4b22f.poster.avif?t=1718141187\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046400/extras/25672758a6bd2aab40b8158699c4b22f.webm?t=1718141187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=